              <div class="flex justify-between px-4 py-3">
                <span class="text-[11px] text-white/30">Pago</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] text-white/60 text-right" id="previewPayment">—</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between px-4 py-3">
                <span class="text-[11px] text-white/50 font-medium">Total</span>
                <span class="text-base font-bold text-accent font-mono" id="previewTotal">$0</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="border border-accent/10 p-4 hidden lg:block">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" class="text-accent shrink-0 mt-0.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"/></svg>
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs text-white/40 leading-relaxed font-body">El contrato se generará automáticamente con los datos ingresados y se enviará al cliente para su firma electrónica.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
